HEY, F-LIST. For those of you not in , it's that time of year for...
FOURTH WALL DAY!
For those of you who've never done a fourth wall before, the basic idea is that for two days (November 16th and 17th) ANYONE is welcome into Discedo for tagging and funtimes! The main guidelines can be found here and here. So, bust out the crackjournals, your main journals, go make someone uncomfortable or bust through the walls like the Kool-Aid Man! (Or maybe be the Kool-Aid Man. That works too.) If you want a simple way to surf through all the journals (because you don't know which ones to stalk properly), you can go to the main comm and look at their friends page. It has all the journals listed so it's easy to find. SO COME JOIN US BLAH BLAH BLAH my posts for my two characters are here: Namine and Italy Have fun! :D

Of course, all music is beautiful. It's really hard picking just two. |D
